                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Chargé <persName type="to">Hutchinson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-11-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 26, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Loomis states that the Department’s request to the Venezuelan Government to
                    instruct its attorney-general to move the court to discharge the receiver is
                    consistent with and stands with the Department’s request for prompt and
                    impartial trial and decision.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
